Package edu.ncsu.csc216.service_wolf.model.manager

Class ServiceWolfManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.service_wolf.model.manager.ServiceWolfManager
  • public class ServiceWolfManager
extends java.lang.Object
    A concrete class that maintains a list of ServiceGroups, the active or current serviceGroup, and handles events from the GUI. ServiceWolf implements the Singleton Design Pattern and is accessed through the getInstance method.
    Author:
    Meles Meles
